'''Caleb''' is one of the doctors who was interviewed to replace Naomi.

==History==
Caleb interviewed for a job at [[Seaside Health and Wellness]]. He'd graduated medical school in three years and did an endocrinology residency in four. The doctors interviewing him were startled by his super enthusiastic energy, fueled by coffee.

[[Jake Reilly]] was ultimately hired for the position.

==Career==
He is an endocrinologist.
